[Pirateat40](https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?action=profile;u=35827) AKA Pirate AKA Trendon Shaver.

Operator of the largest scam in bitcoin history - he operated a [ponzi scheme](https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=50822.0) which guaranteed a daily profit of 1%, and then disappeared with an unknown about of bitcoins on August 2012 (thought to be about 500,000 bitcoins, estimated worth around $5,000,000 at the time).

